    <activity>
        <statement>
            <p>
                <term>Work in Groups to:</term>
            </p>
            <p>
                Measure the length and width of an English textbook and record in the table below.
            </p>
            <tabular top="medium" bottom="medium" left="medium" right="medium">
                <row header="yes">
                    <cell>Side</cell>
                    <cell>Measurent (cm)</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>Length</cell>
                    <cell>?</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>Width</cell>
                    <cell>?</cell>
                </row>
            </tabular>
            <p>
                <term>Find and calculate</term>
            </p>
            <p>
                <ol marker="(a)">
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            The smallest unit of measurement.
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            The maximum and minimum errors of;
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <ol marker="(i)">
                                <li>
                                    <p>
                                        Length
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p>
                                        Width
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                            </ol>
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            Record the values obtained in the table below
                        </p>
                        <tabular top="medium" bottom="medium" left="medium" right="medium">
                            <row header="yes">
                                <cell>Side</cell>
                                <cell>Actual Measurement</cell>
                                <cell>maximum Measurement</cell>
                                <cell>minimum Measurement</cell>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <cell>Length</cell>
                                <cell>?</cell>
                                <cell>?</cell>
                                <cell>?</cell>
                            </row>
                             <row>
                                <cell>Width</cell>
                                <cell>?</cell>
                                <cell>?</cell>
                                <cell>?</cell>
                            </row>
                        </tabular>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </p>
            <p>
                <term>Additional Exploration: </term> In groups find;
            </p>
            <p>
                <ol>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            Sum of actual length and;
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <ol marker="(i)">
                                <li>
                                    <p>
                                        Actual width
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p>
                                        Maximum width
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p>
                                        Minimum width
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                            </ol>
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            Sum of maximum length and;
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <ol marker="(i)">
                                <li>
                                    <p>
                                        Actual width
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p>
                                        Maximum width
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p>
                                        Minimum width
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                            </ol>
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            Sum of minimum length and;
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <ol marker="(i)">
                                <li>
                                    <p>
                                        Actual width
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p>
                                        Maximum width
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p>
                                        Minimum width
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                            </ol>
                        </p>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </p>
            <p>
                From the additional exploration above, what is?
            </p>
            <p>
                <ol marker="(a)">
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            The maximum sum
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            The minimum sum
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            The actual sum (use the formula:)
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <md>
                                <mrow> \text{actual sum} = \amp \; \text{actual length} + \text{actual width} </mrow>
                            </md>
                            
                        </p>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </p>
            <p>
                <term>Subtraction Exploration: </term> In groups find;
            </p>
            <p>
                <ol>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            The difference between actual length and;
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <ol marker="(i)">
                                <li>
                                    <p>
                                        Actual width
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p>
                                        Maximum width
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p>
                                        Minimum width
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                            </ol>
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            The difference between maximum length and;
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <ol marker="(i)">
                                <li>
                                    <p>
                                        Actual width
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p>
                                        Maximum width
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p>
                                        Minimum width
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                            </ol>
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            The difference between minimum length and;
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <ol marker="(i)">
                                <li>
                                    <p>
                                        Actual width
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p>
                                        Maximum width
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p>
                                        Minimum width
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                            </ol>
                        </p>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </p>
            <p>
                From the subtraction exploration above, what is?
            </p>
            <p>
                <ol marker="(a)">
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            The maximum difference
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            The minimum difference
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            The actual difference (use the formula:)
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <md>
                                <mrow> \text{actual difference} = \amp \; \text{actual length} - \text{actual width} </mrow>
                            </md>
                            
                        </p>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </p>
            <p>
                <term>Calculate stepwise the following:</term>
            </p>
            <p>
                <ol marker="(a)">
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            Absolute error in the addition of the length and width?
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            The relative error in the addition of length and width?
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            The percentage error in the addition of length and width?
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            The absolute error in the difference between length and width?
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            The relative error in the difference between length and width?
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            The percentage error in the difference between length and width?
                        </p>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </p>
            <p>
                <term>Discuss and share with other Groups</term>
            </p>
            <p>
                The pattern you notice in the addition and subtraction of errors?
            </p>
        </statement>
    </activity>

